<p><img src="/media/13067550/ski-canada-inghams-canada-month.jpg" alt="Inghams Canada Month" data-udi="umb://media/41bf200bef60466797b62de1a76f0979" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Canada has some of the greatest ski resorts on the planet. The Canadian ski experience is unique, and if you’ve not experienced it for yourself, now is the time to go! Inghams travels to seven of the best ski resorts in Canada, from iconic West Coast gems like <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler </a></strong>to the beautiful Quebecoise resort of <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10}" title="Mont Tremblant">Tremblant</a></strong>.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/761d4a0a1d3f4fa697273a7ee5397a92" href="/{localLink:umb://document/761d4a0a1d3f4fa697273a7ee5397a92}" title="Alberta Ski Offers"><strong><span class="geolocation-title">Discover ski resorts in Alberta, Canada</span></strong></a></p>
