<p><span class="page-title"><strong>Canada Month – Special Offer</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13067547/ski-canada-inghams-canada-month-special-offer.jpg" alt="Ski Canada Special Offer" data-udi="umb://media/c5843f7fb21749358ae31ee537fc6b42" /></p>
<p>This month is Canada Month at Inghams and to celebrate we’re offering our guests the chance to ski in Banff and Whistler for less. For one month only, we’ve taken 20% off the price of the Tri-Area lift pass in <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff"><strong>Banff</strong> </a>and <a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise"><strong>Lake Louise</strong></a>, and 20% off the price of the Whole Area pass in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler"><strong>Whistler</strong></a>.</p>
<p>What is more, we are offering £50 per person off the selected hotels in Banff and Whistler. Book before the 30 April to take advantage of our brilliant Canada Month offers.</p>
