<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="geolocation-title"><a name="Canada_Month"></a>Canada Month Offer Terms and Conditions</span></p>
<p>Canada Month Offer is subject to availability and valid on new bookings made between 29 March - 30 April 2018 only.</p>
<p>£50 per person off your booking applies to the following selected accommodation only: The Banff Inn Hotel, and The Caribou Lodge in Banff, and the Coast Blackcomb Suites, and the Crystal Lodge in Whistler.</p>
<p>20% off lift passes are applicable to the Whistler Whole Area Lift Pass and the Tri-Area Lift Pass in Banff and Lake Louise only. Lift passes must be added to your booking before the 30 April and the offer applies to new bookings only made between 29 March and 30 April 2018.</p>
